reviewText: Very pleased with the DVD as well as with the seller.
Serena + tennis = wonderful!  If you like the tennis sport, you cannot help but to love Serena Williams .
I'm happy that 2010 Wimbeldon final is on dvd. but they should have the Isner VS Mahut 2nd round match.  It's the Greatest match ever. They probably won't do it because it's not the the finals
